  </chunk>
  <chunk id="f582baa8aa4a5f3af8356e86df3d5c29ff426c85.c5" text="2. The authors have demonstrated that Z2 peptide can interact with ZIKV E protein expressed in the uninfected 293T cells. However, it is unclear whether Z2 can interact with the ZIKV surface protein (E/M) dimer . I would suggest the authors to show whether Z2 peptide can interact with the ZIKV surface protein expressed on the ZIKV-infected BHK21 cells.">
